  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个FinTech系统的核心流程图，主要展示交易从进入到最终支付的流转路径。第一个节点应该是交易队列，用来接收所有进来的请求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，交易队列作为入口。那队列之后直接对接支付网关，还是中间需要经过账务处理？FinTech场景里通常会有账本服务来做记账和对账。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，你说得对，中间必须加一层LedgerService。交易队列先把请求推送给账本服务做记录，账本确认后再转发给支付网关执行扣款。这样才是合规的流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把三个节点按从左到右的顺序布局：TransactionQueue → LedgerService → PaymentGateway。方向用LR横向流程，符合阅读习惯。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "方向没问题。不过LedgerService到PaymentGateway的箭头，我需要确认一下——这是单向推送还是双向确认？从业务上看应该是单向的，账本记录完成后异步通知网关。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "目前我画的是单向箭头。如果后续需要展示支付结果回写账本，我们可以改成双向或者增加返回路径。现在保持单向可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "先保持单向，这个版本聚焦主流程。另外，TransactionQueue到LedgerService的连接，我想标注一下是批量推送还是实时推送，不过先不展开细节了，节点命名保持简洁。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整，三个节点现在用实线箭头串联，无额外标注。整体结构是：TransactionQueue作为起点，中间LedgerService处理记账，终点PaymentGateway完成支付。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，这个流程图准确反映了我们系统的核心链路。后续版本可以考虑在LedgerService旁边增加一个异常处理分支，但目前这个结构已经满足评审需求。",
      "elements_involved": [
